OL,3,C'They sold me a dream': Botched Turkey
OL,4,Csurgery patients left with 'no support'
OL,6,FITV News heard from two patients who
OL,7,Ftravelled to Turkey for weight loss
OL,8,Fprocedures and are still living with
OL,9,Fthe consequences, as Geraint Vincent
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FPlastic surgery is a serious business.
OL,13,FIt invariably involves incisions. Very
OL,14,Foften the plastic surgeon is putting
OL,15,Fsomething in, or taking something out,
OL,16,Fof the patient's body.
OL,18,FThe risk of a wound not healing, and
OL,19,Fof subsequent infection, is very real.
OL,20,FSo aftercare is enormously important.
