OL,3,C'They sold me a dream': Botched Turkey
OL,4,Csurgery patients left with 'no support'
OL,6,FThe main attraction of travelling to
OL,7,FTurkey to have plastic surgery is the
OL,8,Fprice. You can have your tummy tuck in
OL,9,FTurkey for as little as a quarter of
OL,10,Fthe cost of the equivalent procedure
OL,11,Fin the UK.
OL,13,FNot worrying too much about aftercare
OL,14,Fis one way some clinics in Turkey can
OL,15,Foffer surgery at such a competitive
OL,16,Fprice.
OL,18,FThe consequences can be dreadful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
