OL,6,FIf you have information about this
OL,7,Fstory or others on the issue please
OL,8,Fcontact us at investigations@itv.com
OL,10,FChristian Richards travelled to Turkey
OL,11,Ffor a range of treatments -
OL,12,Fliposuction, tummy tuck and the
OL,13,Fremoval of fat from his chest.
OL,15,FHe felt something was wrong
OL,16,Fimmediately after the surgery, but
OL,17,Fwhen he got back to the UK he told ITV
OL,18,FNews that he developed a hard lump in
OL,19,Fhis abdomen, which was the size and
OL,20,Fshape of an American football.
