OL,3,C'They sold me a dream': Botched Turkey
OL,4,Csurgery patients left with 'no support'
OL,6,FCourtney Rowley was advised to have
OL,7,Fgastric band surgery by doctors in the
OL,8,FUK because a hormone imbalance led to
OL,9,Fher putting on a lot of weight.
OL,11,FShe went to Turkey for the procedure
OL,12,Fbecause the waiting times were so long
OL,13,Fhere. When she came home she felt
OL,14,Fworse with every day that went by,
OL,15,Funtil eventually, she couldn't stand
OL,16,Fup.
OL,18,FA lack of nutrition meant that she'd
OL,19,Fsuffered terrible nerve damage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
