OL,6,FShe told ITV News there was no
OL,7,Faftercare programme offered by her
OL,8,Fclinic - she should have had a blood
OL,9,Ftest early in her recovery, and
OL,10,Fprobably some vitamin injections.
OL,12,FShe is in a wheelchair now, awaiting
OL,13,Fphysiotherapy on her wasted muscles.
OL,15,F"My consultants say I shouldn't blame
OL,16,Fmyself," Courtney said. "But I do."
